hopobject.body: Could I have an application form? triangle medical park durham nc Walt Disney Co. has indefinitely delayed the planned summer 2015 release of “Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales,” the fifth film in the action series. The movie is being produced by Jerry Bruckheimer, whose latest Disney film, “The Lone Ranger,” flopped with audiences this summer. The latest “Pirates,” set to again star Johnny Depp, was scheduled to open July 10, 2015. Disney didn’t provide an explanation.
